From 328eda010e2db49ed59d53e6c83d3573566c448d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: roku <Thunderoar>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 20:30:12 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 7/8] perf: cache SharedPreferences via lazy-initialized static
 field in Pref class

Adds getSharedPreferences() helper that caches the result in a static
field appSharedPreferences. All MenuValue/setValue methods now use the
cached prefs instead of calling createPackageContext() on every invocation.
Also caches Resources as a bonus.
---
 smali_classes3/com/Fix/Pref.smali | 257 +++++++-----------------------
 1 file changed, 59 insertions(+), 198 deletions(-)

